extendedInfo.description: First Aid Ireland Pop Quiz AppDeveloped by First Aid Ireland, the only provider of Doctor-led first aid training in Ireland.The pop quiz app helps you to test your first aid knowledge from your own phone. Remember that proper training is essential in order to keep your first-aid skills up to date. This app is no substitute for attending a class!All questions in this app have been written by one of our medically qualified instructors.Good luck and enjoy!

reviews.title: Very useful
reviews.comment: Thanks for this great app. Very handy for a quick first aid pop quiz when preparing for First Aid exams. Looking forward to more questions.
reviews.author: A Google User
